  "body": "tslint has been deprecated for some time, and the typescript ecosystem is moving to eslint. We should do it too.\r\n\r\nWe use a few non-standard rules that may make the migration harder. They are:\r\n* [`only-buidler-error`](https://github.com/nomiclabs/buidler/blob/1974956585b4d6ae240bdb3ec50e31d7f478a1dc/packages/buidler-core/tslint/onlyBuidlerErrorRule.ts)\r\n* [`naming-convention`](https://github.com/ajafff/tslint-consistent-codestyle/blob/master/docs/naming-convention.md)\r\n* [`no-unnecessary-else`](https://github.com/ajafff/tslint-consistent-codestyle/blob/master/docs/no-unnecessary-else.md)\r\n\r\n",
